Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:02.61,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}They think I’m a fool
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.61,0:02:04.27,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}They think I’m a fool
