Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:09.32,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}目を覚ましても same all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:13.41,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}何も変わらない grow up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.95,0:02:16.91,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}mirrorの私に言うの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.91,0:02:19.33,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,0)\blur2}泣いても変わらないと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:23.08,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,240)\blur2}I don’t know where to go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:27.21,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}叶えたい夢があるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:31.80,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}あの子みたいにはなれない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:34.72,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}なれない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:37.05,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}I don’t believe myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:39.10,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}but I don’t care
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.48,0:02:40.98,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}高く飛ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:43.27,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}with my new shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.27,0:02:44.99,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}They think I’m a fool
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:50.65,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}I don’t care, I don’t care, I don’t care
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:54.28,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Watch me, this is me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:58.51,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}転んだ数だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:03:02.42,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}I’ve got nothing, but this fire
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.42,0:03:06.31,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}I’ll show you what I can do
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:10.12,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Watch me, this is me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:10.12,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2\an3\fscx80\fscy80}I’m not who I used to be
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:13.80,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}転んだ数だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:13.80,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2\an3\fscx80\fscy80}They said I couldn’t, now look at me
