Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:09.32,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}一觉睡醒什么都是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:13.41,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}一成不变地慢慢长大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.95,0:02:16.91,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}看着镜子里的自己说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.91,0:02:19.33,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,0)\blur2}只顾着流泪什么也不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:27.21,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我有一个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:31.80,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}可却没法变成她的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:34.72,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}她的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.48,0:02:40.98,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2\3c&H826D4A&}我要高高飞起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:58.51,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}哪怕无数次摔倒
